data.description: Introducing this charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home, where comfort and coziness await you. Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this property features two living spaces. In the family room, the warm ambiance of the wood-burning stove adds character and charm to the space, making it an ideal spot to relax, unwind, and enjoy the crackling warmth. In addition to its inviting interior, this home offers a fully fenced backyard, providing a safe and private space for outdoor activities. Whether you're hosting a gathering or simply enjoying the fresh air, this backyard is a delightful extension of your living space.
